// const imgCdn = "https://res.cloudinary.com/swiggy/image/upload/fl_lossy,f_auto,q_auto,w_508,h_320,c_fill/";
const imgCdn = "https://media-assets.swiggy.com/swiggy/image/upload/fl_lossy,f_auto,q_auto,w_300,h_300,c_fit/"
const Title = () => {
  return(
   <img className="logo" alt="logo" src={logo} /> 
  );
}

const NavComponent = () => {
  return (
    <div className="nav-items">
    <ul>
      <li>Home</li>
      <li>About</li>
      <li>Contact</li>
      <li>Cart</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  );
}
const Header = () => {
  return (
    <div className="header">
      <Title />
      <NavComponent />
    </div>
  );
};

const RestaurantCard = ({ name, cuisines, cloudinaryImageId, avgRating, lastMileTravelString }) => {
  console.log("url ::",imgCdn + cloudinaryImageId);

  return (
    <div className="card">
      <img src={ imgCdn + cloudinaryImageId } alt={name} />
      <span className="card-title">{name}</span>
      <span className="card-tags">{cuisines.join(", ")}</span>
      <span className="card-rating">{avgRating}</span>
      <h4>{lastMileTravelString} minutes</h4>
    </div>
  );
};

 
const RestaurantList = () => {
  return (
    <div className="restaurant-list">
      {restaurantList.map((restaurant) => {
        return <RestaurantCard {...restaurant.data} key={restaurant.data.id} />;
      })}
    </div>
  );
}

const Body = () => {
  return (
    <RestaurantList />
  );
};

const Footer = () => {
  return <h4>Footer</h4>;
};

const AppLayout = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Header />
      <Body />
      <Footer />
    </>
  );
};

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById("root"));

root.render(<AppLayout />);
